About us

Our mission at ProducerSources is to empower Music Producers by providing the best tools and knowledge as well as helping them grow their business.

We offer Selected and Discounted High Quality Sound kits, Loops, Midis, VST Plugins and Presets.

Based in New York and Dubai, our products inspire more than 30,000 music producer from the two parts of the world and our platform is known for its best deals and customer service.
